Class OrganizationSelection

  • entity.OrganizationSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bean, Versionable

    public class OrganizationSelection
implements Bean, Versionable
    Wraps an Organization for use with the group picker. This is an internal, transitional entity and the system does not store it in the database.
